129
00:03:20.300 --> 00:03:24.140
The next time you try
and lay your hands on my money,

130
00:03:24.480 --> 00:03:27.810
I'll sell your organs!

131
00:03:29.230 --> 00:03:32.980
If you can't pay me back,
I'll settle for your clothes!

