I guess neither you nor the Flower Capital
can handle me any longer!

664
00:21:07.370 --> 00:21:08.960
I accept the disownment!

665
00:21:09.460 --> 00:21:13.290
Then I shall go! When night falls,
wherever I am is where I sleep!

666
00:21:13.630 --> 00:21:16.130
Ah, a meal would be nice!

667
00:21:17.050 --> 00:21:22.800
What became known as the Day of the
Mountain God occurred during Oden's youth.

668
00:21:24.470 --> 00:21:26.470
Are you crying, Kin?

669
00:21:26.470 --> 00:21:27.890
I'm not crying at all!

670
00:21:28.600 --> 00:21:32.020
Otsuru, I would die for him!

671
00:21:32.020 --> 00:21:33.060
You are crying!

672
00:21:33.060 --> 00:21:34.110
Me too!

673
00:21:34.110 --> 00:21:35.900
I would die for him!

674
00:21:36.270 --> 00:21:37.150
Hey!

675
00:21:37.150 --> 00:21:38.190
Wait, Denjiro!

676
00:21:38.190 --> 00:21:39.440
Oh, Kin!

677
00:21:39.950 --> 00:21:42.700
Kozuki Oden! Kozuki Oden! Kozuki Oden!

678
00:21:42.700 --> 00:21:44.320
He really is incredible!

679
00:21:44.320 --> 00:21:45.580
I've decided!

680
00:21:45.580 --> 00:21:47.790
I'm gonna follow him for the rest of my life!

681
00:21:49.040 --> 00:21:50.790
I wanted to follow him first!

682
00:21:50.790 --> 00:21:53.670
Not as much as me!
I'm his number one follower!

683
00:21:54.790 --> 00:21:57.210
I wish I was free like them!

684
00:21:57.210 --> 00:22:01.970
It's said that because all
the men took a step forward,

685
00:22:01.970 --> 00:22:06.510
but kept themselves from following Oden,
the capital tilted forward slightly...

686
00:22:09.520 --> 00:22:14.350
<b>Hakumai</b>

687
00:22:11.180 --> 00:22:12.810
Please come in, Lord Oden!

688
00:22:12.810 --> 00:22:14.350
What an honor to meet you!

689
00:22:14.770 --> 00:22:17.690
Lord Yasuie has been waiting for you!

690
00:22:17.690 --> 00:22:20.070
Lies do not become us!

691
00:22:20.070 --> 00:22:25.530
<b>Shimotsuki Yasuie

Daimyo of Hakumai</b>

692
00:22:21.070 --> 00:22:25.530
Indeed! Why would I wait to see a fool
who was expelled from the capital?!

693
00:22:25.870 --> 00:22:29.240
What do you want, Oden?! Do you think
your fans make you noteworthy?

694
00:22:29.240 --> 00:22:30.580
Hey, Uncle!

695
00:22:30.950 --> 00:22:32.460
Stop calling me that!

696
00:22:33.710 --> 00:22:35.960
Oh, wait! There is a puddle of water!

697
00:22:38.130 --> 00:22:43.050
Please walk on me to cross over!

698
00:22:43.970 --> 00:22:46.550
He is starting to creep me out!

699
00:22:46.550 --> 00:22:49.350
He is a new servant.

700
00:22:49.680 --> 00:22:50.640
That's right!

701
00:22:50.640 --> 00:22:53.230
Lord Yasuie took me in!

702
00:22:53.230 --> 00:22:57.690
<b>Kurozumi Orochi</b>

703
00:22:54.230 --> 00:22:57.690
I am his servant, Orochi.
